duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide excellent customer service skills in the landscape industry.
Demonstrate strong knowledge of landscape maintenance on job sites.
Provide training, coaching, development, and support for team members on-the-job.
Ensure that accounts are kept on schedule and on budget, coordinating and collaborating with others as needed.
Ensure that team members follow all safety procedures and report unsafe conditions immediately.
Manage reports and reporting on jobs as needed.
